44616029.Line4.EDCC0: Guulrahn is under attack by the Tyrant Brol. Your Lord Overseer commands that you muster the Onyx Watch and ride at once to defend our capital.

5D72A9E6.Line1.EDCC0: To Captain Batai of the Onyx Watch,

784A532D.Line8.EDCC0: - High Captain Tsartu, Guulrahni Royal Guard

DE55D9AB.Line6.EDCC0: I need not remind you of our Lord's opinion of cowards. Those who fail to join in our victory shall be judged in due course.
